name: Red Pill Expo 2021 portrait of the Health Freedom Mamas by Ulysses XYZ
description: Unique digital portrait of Fiorella Trapani, Jill Hines & Melisha Dooley hand-drawn by Ulysses XYZ (uly.xyz) and minted by Volition Labs (volitionlabs.io) on 11/07/2021, the last day of Red Pill Expo 2021 and the 90th birthday of G Edward Griffin.
